It's just I--

181
00:15:35,831 --> 00:15:37,350
我喜欢某种连贯性。
I like a certain coherence.

182
00:15:37,488 --> 00:15:39,524
我不喜欢我喜欢的艺术家
I don't like it when artists I love

183
00:15:39,662 --> 00:15:41,285
在现实生活中表现不好。
don't behave well in real life.

184
00:15:41,423 --> 00:15:43,665
