Oh. Don't wanna see the Bergman Center?

202
00:17:38,264 --> 00:17:40,645
-我明天再看。-好的。
-I'll see it tomorrow. -Okay.

203
00:17:41,784 --> 00:17:42,958
很好。
Fine.

204
00:17:43,683 --> 00:17:44,960
祝你好运。
Good luck.

205
