211
00:21:13,582 --> 00:21:15,653
我说得太多了，但是……
I talked too much, but...

212
00:21:15,791 --> 00:21:18,587
你要喝茶吗?-我想要一些。
-You want some tea? -I'd love some, yeah.

213
